body:
![The Sculkcaller](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d4a89d896da9c66b202cff58f903f2163651f964.png)This mod adds a illager boss called the Sculkcaller:
Mod Creator: Magispeller


- · Has 500 HP (×250) and can deal up to 64 damage with melee attacks, depending on the move;
- · Regenerates 4 HP every second;
- · Commands the power of the deep: summons sculk fangs in a circle or line, and unleashes a devastating sonic boom that deals 10 damage and knocks back enemies;
- · Can summon a loyal Sculk Warden from the ground (once every 300 seconds) to fight by its side;
- · Any nearby warden (natural or summoned) falls under its control, gaining strength and being forced to attack the Sculk Master’s target;
- · While wardens are near, the Sculk Master gains Resistance II;
- · Immune to damage from illagers and all wardens;
- · This boss currently has no custom drops.
